{
  "stem": "25834.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on the wall was-- on the six foot high, you know, the bullet, bullet, and brain-- human brain on the wall and the fragment pieces of the flesh from the shooting.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "X number of people was shot-- created terror.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the reason German doing this, because if one German was killed or something like this, was right away handled.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Polish people was shoot by German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's one reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Other, I was in the place during the day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "German bring maybe 15-- no, 15, maybe 20 people, something like this, and prepare put against the wall, in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the people are not screaming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not give the voice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, what happened?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was watching maybe 50 meter from the 150, 200 foot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And German like you must see what happens if you not listen us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did German do it is put the gypsum in the mouth the people who be shot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And turn their hands like this, and shoot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was, I learn from this moment, the people are doing this way-- not because the people who was shot screaming or holler-- leave-- could leave Poland, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And before was done by Polish guys this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, the German put the gypsum in the mouth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was public execution and mostly was done by SS.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And pick up the people with high education, because these people who was arrested in a special place, later, they were selected-- professor, doctors, Polish or not Polish, Jewish or not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Evangelical and not Evangelical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was not important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Important all professor was killed in Krakow, Warsaw, and also Poznan, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That mean intelligentsia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's German doing first to Polish people, generally speaking.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
